Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.26,0:00:21.00,Title,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(639,303)\fad(417,0)}Mamã e Papá
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.70,0:00:25.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Vou dizer-lhe.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.30,0:00:26.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Hoje é o dia!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.80,0:00:29.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Vou dizer ao Shin-san que gosto dele!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.32,0:00:34.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aquela rapariga...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.58,0:00:36.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,... tinha um ar tão feroz...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.97,0:00:40.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Por momentos, pensei que me fosse bater.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.75,0:00:43.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Voltei!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.78,0:00:44.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mamã!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.53,0:00:47.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Já cheguei, Mao-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.68,0:00:48.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bem-vinda, Honoka.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.69,0:00:51.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Aqui está ele!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.81,0:00:52.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Vou dizer-lhe!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.87,0:01:01.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Afinal não consigo!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.84,0:01:13.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mamã?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.56,0:01:15.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Papá?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.47,0:01:20.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,És muito bom nisto, Mao-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.59,0:01:22.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ei!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.56,0:01:24.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Estão a brincar!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.26,0:01:25.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Papá!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.70,0:01:27.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Talvez me junte a vocês.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.23,0:01:29.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ho—
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.28,0:01:30.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hora da cama!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.37,0:01:35.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mao-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.03,0:01:37.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wai-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.41,0:01:40.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Vamos brincar aos popós!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.47,0:01:42.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A Karin também quer!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.88,0:01:44.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Vamos brincar às bonecas!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.72,0:01:46.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Popós!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.02,0:01:47.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bonecas!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.29,0:01:52.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Estúpidos popós!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.79,0:01:54.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bonecas!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.36,0:01:57.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Popós são divertidos!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.46,0:01:58.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bonecas!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.86,0:02:00.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Popós!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.37,0:02:05.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Odeio-te, Wai-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.04,0:02:08.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ora, ora!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.29,0:02:11.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Brigar é feio.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.31,0:02:13.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Porque não se divertem todos juntos?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.18,0:02:15.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Director...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.34,0:02:17.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Itou-sensei...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.92,0:02:18.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,E agora vamos...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.97,0:02:22.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,... esquecer tudo e dar um aperto de mãos amigável.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.25,0:02:23.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Não!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.35,0:02:24.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, céus!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.72,0:02:26.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Então a Karin-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.79,0:02:29.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,... não lancha...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.08,0:02:33.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aperto de mãos.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.30,0:02:35.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Linda menina!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.93,0:02:41.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Muito bem.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.43,0:02:44.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Agora voltaram a ser bons amigos!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.72,0:02:52.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Não voltei a dirigir palavra ao Shin-san depois daquilo...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.60,0:02:56.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}E estava tão determinada em contar-lhe...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.04,0:02:57.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mamã!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.82,0:03:00.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,O que foi, Mao-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.27,0:03:02.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Por aqui!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.49,0:03:04.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Que se passa?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.72,0:03:10.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mamã!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.88,0:03:13.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Brigar é feio!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.48,0:03:17.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Já sei.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.61,0:03:20.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Está assim porque tenho andado a evitar o Shin-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.06,0:03:24.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Não é nada disso, Mao-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.32,0:03:27.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Não temos andado chateados.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.54,0:03:28.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sério?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.79,0:03:29.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sim!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.49,0:03:30.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A sério!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.96,0:03:31.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,E agora vamos...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.76,0:03:35.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,... esquecer tudo e dar um aperto de mãos amigável.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.93,0:03:36.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aperto de mãos?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.14,0:03:38.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nem pensar!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.26,0:03:41.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Não posso! Não, não, não, não!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.10,0:03:42.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Má menina!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.00,0:03:45.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Se não deres o aperto de mãos, não lanchas.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.06,0:03:47.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mas...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.75,0:03:48.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Honoka...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.84,0:03:53.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Vamos apertar as mãos.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.05,0:03:55.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shin-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.93,0:03:57.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eu...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.15,0:03:59.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,... não gosto de como as coisas têm\N estado ultimamente.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.98,0:04:02.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Não sei se isto é para emendar o assunto,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.11,0:04:03.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,mas por favor, não me evites.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.30,0:04:20.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eu... não sei nada sobre o amor...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.73,0:04:23.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Por isso, não pensei muito na forma como te vejo.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.80,0:04:25.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mas prometo começar a fazê-lo de agora em diante!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.33,0:04:28.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Shin-san!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.18,0:04:31.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Por isso, até lá...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.58,0:04:33.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,... achas que me podias tratar como de costume?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.39,0:04:35.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Claro!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.80,0:04:38.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mao-chan, voltámos a entender-nos, tal como pediste!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.16,0:04:40.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sim!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.43,0:04:42.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}E assim
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.49,0:04:44.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}o meu drama sobre como contaria o que sentia
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.42,0:04:46.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}chegou ao fim.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.40,0:04:52.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mas ele disse que pensaria sobre o que sente por mim.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.32,0:04:54.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Vou andar super nervosa todos os dias!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.57,0:04:57.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mamã?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.15,0:04:59.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,


